## Portfolio Reading

The portfolio is no longer mostly conceptual. Most nuclei have at least D2 local product functionality, five nuclei show D3 integrated functionality, and ACS is registered at D3+ from validated non-production integration evidence. No nucleus is assigned D4 or D5 because this baseline does not find explicit portfolio approval for controlled execution or production capability.
